SUMMARY:Dance With Space
DESCRIPTION:Five decades inside a form leaves its knowledge in the body. This evening\, Malavika Sarukkai brings it to you. \nOne of India’s foremost Bharatanatyam artistes\, Sarukkai presents a selection of her choreographies alongside the creative process that shaped them\, the layering of intention and intuition\, the place where classical grammar meets a contemporary mind. Accompanied by four musicians\, she moves between demonstration and reflection\, making visible what usually remains privy to the artist alone. \nThe evening is open to all: rasikas\, dancers\, scholars\, and enthusiasts alike. \nPhoto credits: Mayur Channagere \nManaged by Shreya Nagarajan Singh Arts Development Consultancy. \nSupported by: \n \n
URL:https://bangaloreinternationalcentre.org/event/dance-with-space/
LOCATION:Bangalore International Centre\, 7\, 4th Main Road\, Domlur II Stage\, Bangalore\, Karnataka\, 560071\, India
CATEGORIES:Dance,Performing Arts
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://bangaloreinternationalcentre.org/wp-content/uploads/Thumbnail_DwS.jpg
END:VEVENT
