UID:86080-1772650800-1772656200@bangaloreinternationalcentre.org
SUMMARY:Colors of Hindustani Slide Guitar
DESCRIPTION:The slide guitar was not born into Hindustani classical music. Joel ‘Veena’ Eisenkramer has spent a lifetime bringing it home. \nEisenkramer has spent decades inside the Hindustani oral tradition\, in conversation with musicians\, collecting the stories and lore that live between the notes. This evening\, he brings all of it to the stage: traditional ragas and original compositions\, interwoven with stories told as they were meant to be\, spoken and spontaneous. Anand HS accompanies on tabla. \nAn evening that asks something of the listener\, and returns considerably more. \nSupported by: \n \n
URL:https://bangaloreinternationalcentre.org/event/colours-of-hindustani-slide-guitar/
LOCATION:Bangalore International Centre\, 7\, 4th Main Road\, Domlur II Stage\, Bangalore\, Karnataka\, 560071\, India
CATEGORIES:Music,Performing Arts
